tags.name: Camp Lonesome Conservation Area
tags.note: Part of a prairie type ecosystem, this conservation area is a diverse mosaic of mixed hardwood and pine forests, native range and dry prairie, palm and oak hammocks, cypress wetlands and grassland. A portion of the property is improved pasture.
